<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,332,893,918]" pageId="14" pageNumber="215">Discussion.</emphasis>
This species group occurs in 
<collectingCountry box="[665,747,893,918]" name="Taiwan" pageId="14" pageNumber="215">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
and southern part of Guangxi.
</paragraph>
